{"tid":785234,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴諷刺曼城:紀錄片都靠我賣錢 該給點版稅","createTime":"2018-08-19T04:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T13:40:38.000Z","uid":147522,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"29d9d6e80a93a8d4ea06333230e41f51bf00962b","tid":785234,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"　　曼城的奪冠紀錄片《All or Nothing》第二集中，專門講述了去年12月曼城在奧脫福擊敗曼聯的比賽，並諷刺了摩連奴的足球風格。摩連奴也被問到了對此的看法，摩帥饒有興致的調侃諷刺了一把曼城。<br />\n<br />\n　　接受採訪時摩帥被問到為何自己會出現在曼城的紀錄片中，摩帥回應：「你們知道吧，如果沒有我，這電影可能賣不了那麼多，所以我必須在那啊。我還沒看過，但聽說了一些電影的事情。我的第一反應是如果你是一家富有的球會，你可以買頂級球員，但買不到風度。這是我的第一反應。」<br />\n<br />\n　　摩帥繼續調侃道：「我的第二反應是，既然我出現在了電影里，我可以要點版稅吧。我不知道，但如果曼城能給我一件T恤，就是他們在球員通道里掛的，上面寫了&lsquo;我們在打比日做到了&rsquo;的那件，那我的版稅就不要好了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　摩帥顯然很有深意，雖說上季曼城在曼聯主場贏了球，但二番戰，曼聯也在曼城的主場逆轉取勝，還破壞了曼城提前奪冠的願望。"},{"pid":"f9f688a0f7e0266d835ac318c53e1202f630871b","tid":785234,"uid":54264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T04:56:19.000Z","msg":"魔性"},{"pid":"71ad559a77e5620b4df86bdb4f16e91bc42a2a6f","tid":785234,"uid":19889,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:06:06.000Z","msg":"摩佬講野真係愈黎愈痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d07283ad127ee77be869b0b7dff4895c14293f","tid":785234,"uid":141543,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"摩佬呢啲咪叫有話題性，marketing一流"},{"pid":"4f2b8c02fd4c881b0c660a8560350bf18fc0cabf","tid":785234,"uid":51121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"呢番說話度都度唔到 佢係幾醒"},{"pid":"116caa9efaa9469d436b0b99217e5180ddf3bd4e","tid":785234,"uid":13320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"你個撚樣都知咩叫風度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eebf4dbc3fc4fc2bc8aae3cb8e136919ec5cb34","tid":785234,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾摩狗"},{"pid":"c7236d4e755ca6cce9d53f9b985fc1f7d8b44945","tid":785234,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:58:41.000Z","msg":"好搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649fdcd25530247afd7932dba9e3a4d7c6c5ea91","tid":785234,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"事實係贏左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e493cc784ac559495aff3f6e01b73511cacd53","tid":785234,"uid":114027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:35:12.000Z","msg":"幾年前都仲串得起，而家就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1831831decdef284d438c65194ab9329a9d7effa","tid":785234,"uid":32947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"識自嘲<br />\n幽自己一默<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7710bb74ad11cb548813873b47bc271ff4b8b5","tid":785234,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T13:40:38.000Z","msg":"10年前摩佬咪又係手執雲爺爺幫佢買好大半既車仔球員玩金錢足球 佢講親咩都可以套返落自己度 屌佢都唔知係真痴定扮傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}